		<section class="article-content__cate"><a href="https://vip.udn.com/vip/cate/121911/121942">生活萬象</a></section>
		<header class="article-content__header">
			<h1 class="article-content__title">別被韓劇騙了！電子門鎖 怕鐵絲更怕駭客</h1>
		</header>
		<figure class="article-content__cover" style="--bg-image: url('https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/02/04/realtime/11485150.jpg&s=Y&x=38&y=218&sw=1134&sh=832&sl=W&fw=800&exp=3600&w=800');">
